      .u-body-copy
        h3.mt2.u-text-center
          strong
            | Tech
        p This campaign is built as a single page web app with a full Javascript tech stack. Sails.js handles the models and controllers on the backend to generate REST API’s while Angular.js handles the views and controllers on the frontend and makes calls to the backend. MongoDB is being used to store data for scaleability.
        p Tech stack: Angular.js, Node.js, Sails.js, Grunt, Bower, mongoDB
        p Full REST API for backend.
